Interface Fragment<NodeType,EdgeType>

public interface Fragment<NodeType,EdgeType>
extends java.util.Collection<Embedding<NodeType,EdgeType>>, Generic<NodeType,EdgeType>, Frequented, java.io.Serializable

This interface describe a special collection for embeddings.

Author:
Marc Woerlein (woerlein@informatik.uni-erlangen.de)
